  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/1de19069cb4bb4842eb6fb091872f48e.avif?t=1761489071\" width=467 height=170 /></span><br>Foxy is a little fox who loves to eat cherries. One day, when he fell asleep, his supplies were stolen!<br><br>Now he has to go through many levels and collect all the cherries to get his supplies back. Embark on an exciting journey through dense jungles, air clouds, and lava caves!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/35ff36c3d5ab6289efb4d550163ecc13.poster.avif?t=1761489071\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/35ff36c3d5ab6289efb4d550163ecc13.webm?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/35ff36c3d5ab6289efb4d550163ecc13.mp4?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To complete all the levels and get your berries back, Foxy will have to show his dexterity, speed, and ability to solve puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/526a8fa93258e35e59b755a473f07242.poster.avif?t=1761489071\" width=516 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/526a8fa93258e35e59b755a473f07242.webm?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/526a8fa93258e35e59b755a473f07242.mp4?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Run, jump, slide on walls, cling to ropes, and dodge various traps and enemies!<br>Collect magic stars on each level that will unlock new characters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/8b652fe0011f9506a12ed913f02371eb.poster.avif?t=1761489071\" width=510 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/8b652fe0011f9506a12ed913f02371eb.webm?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/8b652fe0011f9506a12ed913f02371eb.mp4?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>64 levels with unique challenges and puzzles!<br></li><li>Collect stars to unlock new characters!<br></li><li>Colorful World<br></li><li>Energetic chiptune style music<br></li><li>Collect cherries at each level supplies and advance further</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/1de19069cb4bb4842eb6fb091872f48e.avif?t=1761489071\" width=467 height=170 /></span><br>Foxy is a little fox who loves to eat cherries. One day, when he fell asleep, his supplies were stolen!<br><br>Now he has to go through many levels and collect all the cherries to get his supplies back. Embark on an exciting journey through dense jungles, air clouds, and lava caves!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/35ff36c3d5ab6289efb4d550163ecc13.poster.avif?t=1761489071\" width=506 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/35ff36c3d5ab6289efb4d550163ecc13.webm?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/35ff36c3d5ab6289efb4d550163ecc13.mp4?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>To complete all the levels and get your berries back, Foxy will have to show his dexterity, speed, and ability to solve puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/526a8fa93258e35e59b755a473f07242.poster.avif?t=1761489071\" width=516 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/526a8fa93258e35e59b755a473f07242.webm?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/526a8fa93258e35e59b755a473f07242.mp4?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Run, jump, slide on walls, cling to ropes, and dodge various traps and enemies!<br>Collect magic stars on each level that will unlock new characters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/8b652fe0011f9506a12ed913f02371eb.poster.avif?t=1761489071\" width=510 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/8b652fe0011f9506a12ed913f02371eb.webm?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851270/extras/8b652fe0011f9506a12ed913f02371eb.mp4?t=1761489071\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>64 levels with unique challenges and puzzles!<br></li><li>Collect stars to unlock new characters!<br></li><li>Colorful World<br></li><li>Energetic chiptune style music<br></li><li>Collect cherries at each level supplies and advance further</li></ul>",
